---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
	title="WellRoost | The Decision Engine for Your Home"
	description="WellRoost takes the guesswork out of homeownership with interactive calculators and data-driven insights."
>
	<link slot="head" rel="canonical" href={new URL('/', Astro.site).toString()} />
	
	<!-- Hero Section -->
	<section class="mt-24 sm:mt-32 pb-16 text-center">
		<h1 class="mx-auto max-w-4xl text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-1000 sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl">
			Welcome to WellRoost—<br />
			<span class="text-gray-400">The Decision Engine for Your Home.</span>
		</h1>
		<p class="mx-auto mt-8 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">
			WellRoost takes the guesswork out of homeownership. Built around a core ecosystem of interactive calculators and data-driven insights, we help you make objective, high-ROI choices for your property, budget, and lifestyle.
		</p>
		<p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-3xl text-md leading-7 text-gray-500">
			We don't just give you opinions; we give you the tools to analyze the data. Whether you are weighing a complex "repair vs. replace" dilemma, calculating the payback period of a solar transition, or mapping out the long-term costs of a smart security ecosystem, WellRoost turns complex home logistics into clear, actionable financial choices.
		</p>
		<div class="mt-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-x-6">
			<a href="/calculators/" class="btn-primary">
				Start calculating
			</a>
			<a href="/about/" class="text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-gray-900 transition hover:text-gray-600">
				Learn more <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
			</a>
		</div>
	</section>

	<div class="my-16 border-t border-gray-200"></div>

	<!-- What We Help You Decide -->
	<section class="py-16">
		<div class="mb-12 text-center">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-1000 sm:text-4xl">What We Help You Decide</h2>
		</div>

		<div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
			<!-- Feature 1 -->
			<div class="panel p-8 transition-shadow hover:shadow-md">
				<div class="mb-4 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-gray-100">
					<svg class="h-6 w-6 text-gray-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 7h6m0 10v-3m-3 3h.01M9 17h.01M9 14h.01M12 14h.01M15 11h.01M12 11h.01M9 11h.01M7 21h10a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z" />
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-1000">The Tool Hub</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-600">Interactive, visual calculators that serve as the analytical spine for every project.</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Feature 2 -->
			<div class="panel p-8 transition-shadow hover:shadow-md">
				<div class="mb-4 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-gray-100">
					<svg class="h-6 w-6 text-gray-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-1000">Home Finances</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-600">Clear frameworks for maintenance budgeting, upgrades, and hidden expenses.</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Feature 3 -->
			<div class="panel p-8 transition-shadow hover:shadow-md">
				<div class="mb-4 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-gray-100">
					<svg class="h-6 w-6 text-gray-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-1000">Energy & Tech</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-600">Objective math behind utility savings, smart automation, and hardware interoperability.</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Feature 4 -->
			<div class="panel p-8 transition-shadow hover:shadow-md">
				<div class="mb-4 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-gray-100">
					<svg class="h-6 w-6 text-gray-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M10.325 4.317c.426-1.756 2.924-1.756 3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 002.573 1.066c1.543-.94 3.31.826 2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 001.065 2.572c1.756.426 1.756 2.924 0 3.35a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.066 2.573c.94 1.543-.826 3.31-2.37 2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.572 1.065c-.426 1.756-2.924 1.756-3.35 0a1.724 1.724 0 00-2.573-1.066c-1.543.94-3.31-.826-2.37-2.37a1.724 1.724 0 00-1.065-2.572c-1.756-.426-1.756-2.924 0-3.35a1.724 1.724 0 001.066-2.573c-.94-1.543.826-3.31 2.37-2.37.996.608 2.296.07 2.572-1.065z" />
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
					</svg>
				</div>
				<h3 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-1000">Gear Ecosystems</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-600">Smart evaluations to ensure you invest in the right tools and battery platforms.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Call to Action -->
	<section class="mt-8 mb-24 rounded-2xl bg-gray-1000 p-12 text-center">
		<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl">Stop guessing. Start calculating.</h2>
		<p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-xl text-lg text-gray-300">Welcome to smarter homeownership.</p>
		<div class="mt-8 flex justify-center gap-4">
			<a href="/calculators/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-white px-6 py-3 text-base font-medium text-gray-1000 transition hover:bg-gray-100">
				Browse Calculators
			</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>
